0769">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14975984/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Imaging+spectrum+of+Castleman%27s+disease&amp;author=SF+Ko&amp;author=MJ+Hsieh&amp;author=SH+Ng&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=769-775&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.182.3.1820769&amp;pmid=14975984">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">4.</div><div id="r4" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Johkoh T, Müller NL, Ichikado K, et al. Intrathoracic multicentric Castleman disease: CT findings in 12 patients. <em>Radiology</em> 1998;209(2):477–481.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/radiology.209.2.9807577">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9807577/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Intrathoracic+multicentric+Castleman+disease%3A+CT+findings+in+12+patients&amp;author=T+Johkoh&amp;author=NL+M%C3%BCller&amp;author=K+Ichikado&amp;publication_year=1998&amp;journal=Radiology&amp;pages=477-481&amp;doi=10.1148%2Fradiology.209.2.9807577&amp;pmid=9807577">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Keller AR, Hochholzer L, Castleman B. Hyaline-vascular and plasma-cell types of giant lymph node hyperplasia of the mediastinum and other locations. <em>Cancer</em> 1972;29(3):670–683.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/1097-0142(197203)29:3%3C670::AID-CNCR2820290321%3E3.0.CO;2-%23">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a hre